title: Primordial Matter
tooltip: universal property: difficult to destroy or contaminate natural materials here
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

While on a [[plane]] with this property, it is difficult to destroy or contaminate matter that is native to the plane. All nonmagical food and drink is purified and rendered free of poison and disease. In addition, natural materials such as wood and stone are tougher than their mundane counterparts. 